value.0: Danite is the third most common form of the Adegan Crystals, this crystal doesn't focus energy as well as its rarer cousins, and thus usually reserved for use in training sabers. Adegan crystals are commonly used by Jedi as a main component of a lightsaber. Also known as "Ilum crystals," these rare Force-reactive stones are primarily found in the Adega system, and on the planet Ilum, but are also known to be found on the planet Halm.
